                <label class="step-v2"><input type="checkbox" class="step-v2__checkbox step-checkbox" data-step="d360-m5-s10"><span class="step-v2__text">Configure <strong>CRM Related List</strong>: Add Data 360 component to Contact page to display insight metrics</span></label>
